1. *Velika* površina njenog dvorišta je bila zapanjujuća. (The large surface of her yard was stunning.)

2. Naša *velika* obitelj se često okuplja za vrijeme blagdana. (Our large family often gets together during holidays.)

3. On je postigao *velika* uspjeha u svojoj profesiji. (He achieved great success in his profession.)

4. Ona je izgradila *veliku* kuću na obali. (She built a big house by the shore.)

5. Njegov *veliki* doprinos je bio neprocjenjiv. (His great contribution was invaluable.)